"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-07-90s-sports-icon-responds-calls-make-stunning-olympics-comeback-21377464\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"90s sports icon Tony Hawk has responded to calls urging him to make a stunning comeback in the sport of skateboarding and compete at the nextOlympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 150, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"90s sports icon Tony Hawk\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 25}, {\"ngram\": \"calls\", \"from\": 43, \"to\": 48}, {\"ngram\": \"a stunning comeback\", \"from\": 68, \"to\": 87}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 91, \"to\": 100}, {\"ngram\": \"the nextOlympics\", \"from\": 133, \"to\": 149}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hawk, 56, is the most celebrated skateboarder of all time and played a huge part in putting the sport on the map in the 1990s.\", \"from\": 152, \"to\": 278, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most celebrated skateboarder\", \"from\": 165, \"to\": 197}, {\"ngram\": \"all time\", \"from\": 201, \"to\": 209}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge part\", \"from\": 221, \"to\": 232}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 244, \"to\": 253}, {\"ngram\": \"the map\", \"from\": 257, \"to\": 264}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Described as a 'pioneer' of vertical skateboarding, Hawk won over 50 major competitions and also produced the first ever documented '900 degrees' trick in 1999.\", \"from\": 280, \"to\": 440, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 'pioneer\", \"from\": 293, \"to\": 303}, {\"ngram\": \"vertical skateboarding\", \"from\": 308, \"to\": 330}, {\"ngram\": \"Hawk\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 336}, {\"ngram\": \"over 50 major competitions\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 367}, {\"ngram\": \"the first ever documented '900 degrees' trick\", \"from\": 386, \"to\": 431}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris 2024 Olympics Such was his status in the sport, Hawk even licensed a skateboarding video game series named after him.\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 618, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 472}, {\"ngram\": \"updates\", \"from\": 477, \"to\": 484}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 499}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 513}, {\"ngram\": \"his status\", \"from\": 523, \"to\": 533}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 537, \"to\": 546}, {\"ngram\": \"Hawk\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 552}, {\"ngram\": \"a skateboarding video game series\", \"from\": 567, \"to\": 600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Skateboarding only made its Olympic debut three years ago in Tokyo so Hawk, who retired in 2003, was unable to feature at a Games or secure a medal.\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 768, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 681, \"end\": 686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.977020685286982, \"rank\": 0.02351142551322811, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its Olympic debut\", \"from\": 644, \"to\": 661}, {\"ngram\": \"Hawk\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 694}, {\"ngram\": \"a Games\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 749}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 767}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But viewers have enjoyed seeing the American in and around the skateboarding competition at Paris 2024, with Hawk testing out the course before the event started and working as a TV pundit during the action.\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 977, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 806, \"end\": 814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.7645809287749412, \"rank\": 0.30790476026901564, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"viewers\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 781}, {\"ngram\": \"the skateboarding competition\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 858}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 867}, {\"ngram\": \"Hawk\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 883}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 906}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 923}, {\"ngram\": \"a TV pundit\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 958}, {\"ngram\": \"the action\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 976}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hawk's presence on TV screens has led fans to call for the icon to make an incredible return to the sport but the man in question says he has won 'a golden ticket' with his current role.\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 1165, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hawk's presence\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 994}, {\"ngram\": \"TV screens\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1008}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1021}, {\"ngram\": \"the icon\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1042}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredible return\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1071}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1084}, {\"ngram\": \"the man\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1096}, {\"ngram\": \"question\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1108}, {\"ngram\": \"a golden ticket\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1141}, {\"ngram\": \"his current role\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1164}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked whether he was tempted to come out of retirement and potentially feature at the next Olympics in 2028, Hawk toldBBC Sport: 'I have got the golden ticket.\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1326, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"retirement\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1221}, {\"ngram\": \"the next Olympics\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1266}, {\"ngram\": \"Hawk\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1280}, {\"ngram\": \"Sport\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1294}, {\"ngram\": \"the golden ticket\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1325}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I get to skate the course and watch from upfront - it's amazing!\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1354}, {\"ngram\": \"upfront\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1377}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You see people like Arisa [Trew] and Sky Brown, you see the top field in the men's, it's anyone's game.\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1497, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1414, \"end\": 1419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arisa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.162235056078575e-15, \"text\": \"Arisa\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arisa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arisa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1408}, {\"ngram\": \"the top field\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1463}, {\"ngram\": \"the men\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1474}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone's game\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1496}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Skateboarding legend Tony Hawk is delighted to see the sport at the Olympics \\u00f0\\u009f\\u009b\\u00b9\\u00e2\\u009d\\u00a4\\u00ef\\u00b8\\u008fCould we see him make comeback for the Games?\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1631, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Skateboarding legend Tony Hawk\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1529}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1559}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1575}, {\"ngram\": \"comeback\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1616}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1630}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We had to ask!\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1646, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0091\\u0080#Paris2024#Olympics#BBCOlympicspic.twitter.com/1hQYySZB7b 'I mean, [Team GB skateboarder] Andy MacDonald is here and he's 51!\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1777, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1742, \"end\": 1756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Macdonald_(skateboarder)\", \"score\": 0.7012169389860421, \"rank\": 0.42608695652174866, \"text\": \"Andy MacDonald\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Macdonald_(skateboarder)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Macdonald_(skateboarder)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0091\\u0080#Paris2024#Olympics#BBCOlympicspic.twitter.com/1hQYySZB7b\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1708}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am definitely living vicariously through him.\", \"from\": 1778, \"to\": 1825, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am happy because he's representing you guys but he's also representing our generation.\", \"from\": 1826, \"to\": 1914, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"you guys\", \"from\": 1863, \"to\": 1871}, {\"ngram\": \"our generation\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 1913}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We went through the formative years, we went through the ups and downs - this wasn't cool or even a career choice when we were kids.\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 2049, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the formative years\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 1952}, {\"ngram\": \"the ups\", \"from\": 1970, \"to\": 1977}, {\"ngram\": \"downs\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 1987}, {\"ngram\": \"kids\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2048}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Now look at it, the fact we have someone in the mix that represents how far we have come, that's everything to me.'\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2167, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2092}, {\"ngram\": \"the mix\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2103}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2149, \"to\": 2159}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a separate interview, Hawk added: 'I do not think you want to see me competing when I am 60.\", \"from\": 2169, \"to\": 2264, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a separate interview\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2192}, {\"ngram\": \"Hawk\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2198}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'That's probably not going to bode well.\", \"from\": 2266, \"to\": 2306, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I will definitely be there as a fan.'\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2348, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fan\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2346}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hawk went on to express his delight at how skateboarding has integrated into the Olympics, though he insists the sport did not need any 'validation'.\", \"from\": 2350, \"to\": 2499, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hawk\", \"from\": 2350, \"to\": 2354}, {\"ngram\": \"his delight\", \"from\": 2374, \"to\": 2385}, {\"ngram\": \"how skateboarding\", \"from\": 2389, \"to\": 2406}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2427, \"to\": 2439}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2468}, {\"ngram\": \"any 'validation\", \"from\": 2482, \"to\": 2497}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'This whole movement has been a long time coming,' he said.\", \"from\": 2501, \"to\": 2560, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This whole movement\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2521}, {\"ngram\": \"a long time\", \"from\": 2531, \"to\": 2542}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The Olympics needs our cool-factor more than we needed their validation but the marriage has been very beneficial to everyone.'\", \"from\": 2562, \"to\": 2690, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympics\", \"from\": 2563, \"to\": 2575}, {\"ngram\": \"our cool-factor\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2597}, {\"ngram\": \"their validation\", \"from\": 2618, \"to\": 2634}, {\"ngram\": \"the marriage\", \"from\": 2639, \"to\": 2651}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2680, \"to\": 2688}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hawk's friendAndy MacDonald will represent Great Britain's in the men's skateboarding event on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 2692, \"to\": 2797, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hawk's friendAndy\", \"from\": 2692, \"to\": 2709}, {\"ngram\": \"MacDonald\", \"from\": 2710, \"to\": 2719}, {\"ngram\": \"Great Britain\", \"from\": 2735, \"to\": 2748}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's skateboarding event\", \"from\": 2754, \"to\": 2783}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 2787, \"to\": 2796}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 51-year-old turned out for America for two decades but switched his allegiances earlier this year and was able to do so due to having a British father.\", \"from\": 2799, \"to\": 2954, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2939, \"end\": 2946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9663277695851687, \"rank\": 0.03365602793608362, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 2837}, {\"ngram\": \"two decades\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 2853}, {\"ngram\": \"his allegiances\", \"from\": 2867, \"to\": 2882}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MacDonald will look to secure another skateboarding medal for Team GB after16-year-old Sky Bronze won bronze in the women's competition.\", \"from\": 2956, \"to\": 3092, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3018, \"end\": 3025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999312497548934, \"rank\": 6.875390569265881e-05, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 3043, \"end\": 3046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9999215206931914, \"rank\": 7.835197899141236e-05, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"MacDonald\", \"from\": 2956, \"to\": 2965}, {\"ngram\": \"another skateboarding medal\", \"from\": 2986, \"to\": 3013}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 3058, \"to\": 3064}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's competition\", \"from\": 3068, \"to\": 3091}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'This journey has been crazy w